Plain language summary
Single computer models are often not enough to
describe phenomena and processes across science
and engineering. The software package preCICE
allows programmers and end users to combine
existing models with minimal effort, producing
accurate results and being portable from a laptop
to a large supercomputer. With recent improvements
and extensions in code and user experience, preCICE
is now being sustainably developed and actively used
by a vivid community spanning from aerospace and
biomedical engineering to climate research.

easy-to-use software (with users!)

- Packaging and dependencies: standard and minimal
